snippet.title: Whitelight
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Dark Souls of games media, your #1 source of video game analysis and occasionally, existential crises. 

Merch store with more drip than a neptunian rainstorm (not verified): https://www.whitelight.store/

If you want to contact me, you can send a DM on Discord, or use my email.

Email: WhiteGlass94@gmail.com (General) and whitelightdavid@gmail.com (Business) (whitelightenquiries is a fraud account trying to scam you, believe nothing they send)

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/whitelightYT
